title: Konad Nail Art Double Ended Stamper And Scraper
description:
This stamper has 2 ends with different sizes and colours. Great when stamping small images or for childrens nails. The green stamper is ideal when using red special polish because the red image shows up better on the green stamper.

If you receive it, and like it,please give us good Feedback.

title: China Glaze Nail Polish, Atlantis, 0.5 Fluid Ounce
description: Atlantis is a medium blue or green polish with lots of sparkle and shine. If you are looking for a dazzling, sparkling colored polish you will love this fun and sparkly polish that will really make your nails pop. Long-wearing nail lacquer. Flexible and will not chip. Non-thickening formula no thinner required.
